            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">
              Building modern web applications and AI-powered tools using cutting-edge technologies. 
              Focus on creating practical solutions and contributing to open source projects.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
              <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full font-medium">TypeScript</span>
              <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full font-medium">React</span>
              <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full font-medium">Node.js</span>
              <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full font-medium">AI/ML</span>
