                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 text-green-800 dark:text-green-200 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">Current</span>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">
              Actively pursuing a Computer Science degree with focus on software development, 
              algorithms, and modern web technologies. Eager to apply academic knowledge 
