              <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full font-medium">Data Structures</span>
              <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full font-medium">Web Development</span>
